==Russian==

===Etymology===
For individual etymologies, see the words : [[ездить]] [[в]] [[Тулу]] [[со]] [[своим]] [[самоваром]].  The phrase derives from the fact that [[w:Tula|Tula]] is well-known for [[samovar]].  The phrase was coined by [[w:Chekhov|Chekhov]].

<!-- ===Pronunciation=== -->

===Verb===
'''ездить в Тулу со своим самоваром'''
# {{idiom}} to do something that is not needed (''literally:'' to go to [[w:Tula|Tula]] with [[samovar]]); see [[bring owls to Athens]] and [[carry coals to Newcastle]]
#*''И коллеги удивленно пожимают плечами: В Тулу со своим самоваром?'' [http://www.intertravel.ru/sovet/sovet24.php]
#**''And the colleagues shrug their shoulders: to Tula with the samovar?''

